pullrequest.title: Slimmed down the Plugin pull request (no more template specializations)

content.raw: Ouch, I totally should have realized that would cause it. I now remember running into a similar problem on Linux a while back where it wasn't linking despite the symbol definitely existing. It's weird that the visibility didn't affect Linux this time around.
